description:
Fear, Corruption, War, Propaganda, Media. All these are tools used to control the masses. The elites of the world care for only a few things. The do not care for us as individuals, they care for us as mindless slaves that will keep their system afloat. Most people will refuse to believe that our government is not in favor of the people and politicians, celebrities, athletes, musicians etc... are used to push agendas to the masses.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
One thing we know is... Outside of the television screen WE DO NOT KNOW ANY OF THESE PEOPLE PERSONALLY. What makes you think they care for us. They care for their position in society.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Think about what is going on today. We are on lockdown. They have made a virus less dangerous than the seasonal flu a boogeymen. They media has made people afraid of their loved ones. Wake up this is all an agenda to push for something else.
